      "path": "OperationalHealthSla.SemanticModel/definition/expressions.tmdl",
      "content": "/// Microsoft Entra tenant (directory) ID.\nexpression TenantId = \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\" meta [IsParameterQuery=true, Type=\"Text\", IsParameterQueryRequired=true]\n\tlineageTag: 3c250690-b022-c3e6-5239-ef06311571a7\n\tqueryGroup: 'Parameters'\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Text\n\n/// Azure subscription ID to scope estate queries to.\nexpression SubscriptionId = \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\" meta [IsParameterQuery=true, Type=\"Text\", IsParameterQueryRequired=true]\n\tlineageTag: 4daa36a9-62d1-fbf4-041f-34974558fbff\n\tqueryGroup: 'Parameters'\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Text\n\n/// Cost Management scope (subscription, RG, billing account or MG).\nexpression BillingScope = \"/subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\" meta [IsParameterQuery=true, Type=\"Text\", IsParameterQueryRequired=true]\n\tlineageTag: 9fe4ac38-8120-3fec-a9b4-a2c4f124c4a2\n\tqueryGroup: 'Parameters'\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Text\n\n/// Log Analytics workspace (customer) ID for operational/security logs.\nexpression LogAnalyticsWorkspaceId = \"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\" meta [IsParameterQuery=true, Type=\"Text\", IsParameterQueryRequired=true]\n\tlineageTag: a05219b3-e880-3a58-276f-ed7300776544\n\tqueryGroup: 'Parameters'\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Text\n\n/// ARM endpoint. Gov: https://management.usgovcloudapi.net.\nexpression ManagementApiBase = \"https://management.azure.com\" meta [IsParameterQuery=true, Type=\"Text\", IsParameterQueryRequired=true]\n\tlineageTag: 033facc1-93bc-af39-5411-58bdf9c9bf27\n\tqueryGroup: 'Parameters'\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Text\n\nqueryGroup Parameters\n"
