      "content": "table 'Subscriptions'\n\tlineageTag: 550b8afe-0486-2557-2396-d7728eed5e5d\n\n\tmeasure 'Subscription Conformance' = AVERAGE('Subscriptions'[ConformancePct])\n\t\tformatString: 0.0%\n\t\tlineageTag: 523c8bf1-854e-dba0-1514-4d300a578525\n\n\tmeasure 'Subscription Count' = COUNTROWS('Subscriptions')\n\t\tformatString: #,##0\n\t\tlineageTag: a18a8588-bba2-0136-b820-532f28d881c6\n\n\tcolumn 'SubscriptionName'\n\t\tdataType: string\n\t\tlineageTag: 0794b99c-f9cd-1fb7-056f-ba0b1db09206\n\t\tsummarizeBy: none\n\t\tsourceColumn: SubscriptionName\n\n\t\tannotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic\n\n\tcolumn 'ManagementGroup'\n\t\tdataType: string\n\t\tlineageTag: 40b84101-f60c-bdf2-0ad0-6e653264a882\n\t\tsummarizeBy: none\n\t\tsourceColumn: ManagementGroup\n\n\t\tannotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic\n\n\tcolumn 'Environment'\n\t\tdataType: string\n\t\tlineageTag: fc29df5f-2499-88c3-6ba2-5c0fcc4a1271\n\t\tsummarizeBy: none\n\t\tsourceColumn: Environment\n\n\t\tannotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic\n\n\tcolumn 'ConformancePct'\n\t\tdataType: double\n\t\tlineageTag: 414b895e-c25c-f748-0a7b-69af5d7a1c98\n\t\tsummarizeBy: average\n\t\tsourceColumn: ConformancePct\n\n\t\tannotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic\n\n\tpartition 'Subscriptions' = m\n\t\tmode: import\n\t\tsource =\n\t\t\t\tlet\n\t\t\t\t\t// SAMPLE DATA — replace the \"Source\" step below with the live Azure query.\n\t\t\t\t\t// === Live source (uncomment + remove the sample step) ===\n\t\t\t\t\t// let\n\t\t\t\t\t//     // Azure Resource Graph via ARM REST (AAD/OAuth via the data-source credential).\n\t\t\t\t\t//     Body = \"{\"\"subscriptions\"\":[\"\"\" & SubscriptionId & \"\"\"],\"\"query\"\":\"\"ResourceContainers | where type == 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions' | project SubscriptionName=name, ManagementGroup=tostring(properties.managementGroupAncestorsChain[0].displayName)\"\"}\",\n\t\t\t\t\t//     Resp = Web.Contents(ManagementApiBase & \"/providers/Microsoft.ResourceGraph/resources?api-version=2022-10-01\",\n\t\t\t\t\t//         [Headers=[#\"Content-Type\"=\"application/json\"], Content=Text.ToBinary(Body)]),\n\t\t\t\t\t//     Json = Json.Document(Resp),\n\t\t\t\t\t//     Rows = Table.FromRecords(Json[data])\n\t\t\t\t\t// in\n\t\t\t\t\t//     Rows\n\t\t\t\t\t// === end live source ===\n\t\t\t\t\tSource = #table(\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttype table [#\"SubscriptionName\"=type text, #\"ManagementGroup\"=type text, #\"Environment\"=type text, #\"ConformancePct\"=type number],\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\"mgmt\", \"Platform\", \"platform\", 0.95},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\"connectivity\", \"Platform\", \"platform\", 0.92},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\"prod-platform\", \"Landing Zones\", \"prod\", 0.81},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\"prod-data\", \"Landing Zones\", \"prod\", 0.88},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\"nonprod-dev\", \"Sandbox\", \"dev\", 0.64}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\t)\n\t\t\t\tin\n\t\t\t\t\tSource\n\n\tannotation PBI_ResultType = Table\n"
